{"tha-ap64:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap64:0.2":"Sakacintaniyavagga ","tha-ap64:0.3":"2 Avopupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap64:1.1":"“Vihara abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap64:1.2":"abbhutthasi ca cankame; ","tha-ap64:1.3":"Catusaccam pakasanto, ","tha-ap64:1.4":"desento amatam padam. ","tha-ap64:2.1":"Sikhissa giramannaya, ","tha-ap64:2.2":"buddhasetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap64:2.3":"Nanapuppham gahetvana, ","tha-ap64:2.4":"akasamhi samokirim. ","tha-ap64:3.1":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap64:3.2":"lokajettha narasabha; ","tha-ap64:3.3":"Pattomhi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap64:3.4":"hitva jayaparajayam. ","tha-ap64:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap64:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap64:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap64:4.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap64:5.1":"Ito visatikappamhi, ","tha-ap64:5.2":"sumedho nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap64:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap64:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap64:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap64:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap64:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap64:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma avopupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap64:8.1":"Avopupphiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}